title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Dec 3 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Dec 3 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

Monica Crowley's take on the economy and 2024. Out-of-touch Alec Baldwin blames gun, bashes Trump. Stephen Colbert doesn't understand democracy. Clay complains: Remember when comedians used to be funny? Another Brian Kelly southern accent clip. The accent stinks, and, in all cases -- humorous or not -- Clay reminds us it's better to just be ourselves.
